<p>Centre for Soldiers Wives &amp; Mothers<br/>27.7.16</p>
<p>Dear Mr. Layton &ndash;<br/>Mrs. Davies &amp; 2 children want to get back to her husband who has been returned wounded to Brisbane &amp; has not the means to pay her fare to Brisbane. Can you assist her with her fares for self &amp; 2 children, her pay is only half this time &amp; leaves her without any money when expenses paid that are owing &ndash;</p>
<p>Yours truly<br/>E. H. Bennie.</p>
